  "task_intent": "Zinc metalloenzyme preparation: prepare human carbonic anhydrase II (PDB 2CBA) while retaining the single catalytic Zn2+ as a supported metal ion and keeping its His94/His96/His119 coordination shell, rather than dropping the zinc or treating it as a generic ligand. Neutralize the resulting system.",
